{"tid":2081623,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"四太梁安琪發聲明首認猷邦身份：他注定必須被保護","createTime":"2020-06-27T11:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T13:08:33.000Z","uid":54582,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5224e2c62644811efc242061a9a29f4ac1f760","tid":2081623,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200627/VJ7PQHTQB6M2SLAFQ3ZWW2X6Q4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200627%2FVJ7PQHTQB6M2SLAFQ3ZWW2X6Q4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=9db2989f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200627%2FVJ7PQHTQB6M2SLAFQ3ZWW2X6Q4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=19e44d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200627/VJ7PQHTQB6M2SLAFQ3ZWW2X6Q4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n賭王何鴻燊上月26日於養和醫院病逝，享年98歲。今日何家在報章刊登訃聞，首次見到賭王第六名兒子猷邦名字，在訃聞中，猷邦在子女輩份中排在三房孻仔猷啟之後，四房大仔猷亨之前，估計約28歲。其實多年前，曾傳出與四太還有另一名兒子，當時曾傳出其子叫何猷佳，但一直未有證實，今日四太向傳媒發聲明，首次確認猷邦身份，聲明中承認猷邦出於身體原因，故一直未有向外透露任何關於猷邦的消息。<br />\n<br />\n聲明如下：<br />\n大家好，我是梁安琪。今天，我鄭重地和大家介紹一下何鴻燊先生和我的孩子，不是傳言中的何猷佳，他叫何猷邦。<br />\n<br />\n因為身體的原因，家族從未對外公佈過他的任何信息。由於何先生的不幸離世，按照傳統習俗何猷邦的姓名會鐫刻在他父親的墓碑上。我理解我先生作為公眾人物，他的一切都會被外界關注。但先生和我為猷邦所做出的選擇，也希望得到足夠的尊重與隱私保護。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個母親，我很焦慮外界的不實傳言會帶給猷邦負面的情緒影響。在這樣的家庭想做一個普通人很難，但是作為一個母親仍然希望可以在我們的保護下，讓他感受到外面世界的安全和善良。<br />\n猷邦在何氏家族及親友間並不是一個秘密，從小到大如其他孩子一樣，深受家家人呵護照顧。一直以來我們家都會一起去旅行，舉辦生日會，讓他的生活更快樂。我先生也非常疼愛他，盡量為他做好一切妥善的安排。<br />\n猷邦的人生，注定了他必須被保護，不能夠被打擾。我們知道現實社會生活，需要故事，但亦需要善意、理解、互相的愛護。<br />\n這是我們第一次也是最後一次就此事向公眾說明，萬望大家理解。感謝。"},{"pid":"344d7843a25c7c7db619c2eb9c08de3d4a3881c0","tid":2081623,"uid":140335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:05:32.000Z","msg":"爭家產先出黎<br />\n又可以攞多份"},{"pid":"3c38f354c1eafaa5a595d349b5e009b600ecbb9c","tid":2081623,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:06:11.000Z","msg":"弱智？"},{"pid":"9a8ebc69b6b63816f205881c525a7c3b09b03529","tid":2081623,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"即係智障/自閉"},{"pid":"840b0bf6923d6784da7b2082a0068eca2c535773","tid":2081623,"uid":277186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"講真 其實關其他人撚事？"},{"pid":"5c817fdcf99fd64836bb5dc3de78c60bbdcd09e6","tid":2081623,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"而家先講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5647ebe0cc4199bae77ae457a09bbc7ca5e0c0","tid":2081623,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a8ebc69b6b63816f205881c525a7c3b09b03529","tid":2081623,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"即係智障/自閉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"應該係智力有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059af94c5007554595c8c4fbf134c870a0a42185","tid":2081623,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840b0bf6923d6784da7b2082a0068eca2c535773","tid":2081623,"uid":277186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"講真 其實關其他人撚事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"哽係有人用手段逼佢公開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5a7534975f72899cea29dc4af1a1b60add7754","tid":2081623,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}